 of the Nth BS$\\Delta$E is close to\nthe solution of the BSDE in distribution too.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Feb 2010 03:02:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 23 Jul 2013 13:28:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-07-24"}
