 of the suspension. For the static yield stress, a scaling law\n$\\Phi^\\beta$, with $\\beta = 0.54$, is found. The results are found to be\nreasonably consistent with each other. Their similarities with-, and\ndiscrepancies to- results obtained on laponite-oil suspensions are discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Feb 2010 13:24:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-18"}
